 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

 be an element of the codomain (a function) and set 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=\frac{b(x)}{e^{x}}$
\end_inset

.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula $T(f)=e^{x}\frac{b(x)}{e^{x}}=b(x)$
\end_inset

 so the equation 
\begin_inset Formula $T(a)=b$
\end_inset

 has at least one solution (
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

).
\begin_inset Newline newline
